quran[34]{c,v,t}:
  56,17,Ka bidibbihi (ban bi zoora) guuri gindi ba (Alizanda maa puuni)
  56,18,"(Ka bɛ gili ba) ni kopunima mini jiŋlahi, n-ti pahi jaashee din nyɛ dam, ka zɔri yiri kobilnina shɛŋa ni na"
  56,19,"Zuɣuyaali bi gbaari ba, bɛ mi bi buɣira"
  56,20,Ni binwoli shεŋa bɛ ni gahim (bε ni kuli bɔri shεli) bɛ suhiri ni
  56,21,"Ni noombihi nimdi, ka di nyɛla bɛ suhi ni gbaai shɛli"
  56,22,"Ni (Alizanda) paɣa shεba ban nimbihi pεla, ka galsi galsi"
  56,23,Ka bɛ (Alizanda paɣaba maa) ŋmani alulluɣi shεli din be di waɣu ni
  56,24,Ka di nyɛ sanyoo ni bɛ ni daa tumdi tuun’ shɛŋa
  56,25,"Bɛ bi wumdi yεltɔɣa kaha di puuni, bɛ mi bi kpεri Naawuni taali puuni"
  56,26,"Naɣila bɛ yεrila taba: “Salaaman, salaaman (suhudoo, suhudoo).”"
  56,27,"Ni nudirgunima, bimbo n-leei nyɛ nudirgunima"
  56,28,(Bɛ yɛn ti bela) naɣatibchεriga ti’ shɛli din ka gɔhi gbinni
  56,29,Ni kodu ti’ shεli din mali wola pam
  56,30,Ni mahim din teei bahi luɣuli kam
  56,31,Ni kom din kuli zɔra
  56,32,Ni binwola pam
  56,33,"Di (binwola maa) ka naabu, bɛ mi bi mɔŋdi so di dibu"
  56,34,Ni bindɔhi din du zuɣusaa
  56,35,"Achiika! Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) nam ba mi (Alizanda paɣaba maa), ka di nyɛ nambu ni yɛlimaŋli"
  56,36,"Din nyaaŋa, ka Ti zali ba ka bε nyɛla paɣasara"
  56,37,"Ka bɛ nyɛla ban yuri bɛ yidaannima, ka bɛ yuma lahi saɣisi taba"
  56,38,Ka bɛ nyɛ nudirigunim’ (Alizanda bihi) dini
  56,39,Ka bɛ nyɛ zamaatu pam ban daŋ tooni puuni
  56,40,Ni bahigunim’ (Annabi Muhammadu niriba) puuni pam
  56,41,"Nuzaanim’ mi, bo n-leei nyɛ nuzaa- nima"
  56,42,Bɛ yɛn ti bela pɔhimtulli mini kotulum ni
  56,43,Ni mahim din nyɛ nyɔhi din kuli sabgi
  56,44,"Di ka maasim, di mi ka suhupiɛlli"
  56,45,Achiika! Bɛ daa nyɛla ninvuɣu shεba ban be nyεɣisim puuni pɔi ni dina (Dunia puuni)
  56,46,Yaha! Bɛ daa nyɛla ban kuli bi milgi ka be tuumbiɛri din galsi ni
  56,47,"Yaha! Bɛ daa nyɛla ban yεra: “Di ni bɔŋɔ, ti yi kpi ka leei taŋkpaɣu mini koba, ti nyɛla bɛ ni yɛn tooi lahi yiɣisi shɛba"
  56,48,"“Di ni bɔŋɔ, ni ti banim’ ban daŋ tooni maa gba?”"
  56,49,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yεlima: “Achiika! Ban daŋ tooni mini ban kpalim nyaaŋa maa.”"
  56,50,“Achiika! Bɛ nyɛla bɛ ni yɛn ti laɣim shɛba saha shɛli din nyɛ dabsimirili (dina n-nyɛ Zaadali).”